room_description: You wake up to find yourself in what seems to be a hospital room. You soon realize that you've been abducted by Maggie who is a former patient of Oktibbeha county insane asylum. The asylum was shut down due to numerous patients disappearing and never being found. Maggie has been hiding out in the asylum for years and believes she is a psychiatrist. She has chosen you as her patient, locked you in her old room, and wants to see if your manipulative behavior can help you con your way out. You have 60 minutes to master her game and prove your sanity before she deems you one of her patients for eternity.
